text:
Mano, sorry to keep you waiting!
Shall we start the meeting?

Ah, um, sorry...!
I left the outfit I received just lying there...
It was in the way, I'll move it right away.

...N-No,
it's not bothering at all, so it's okay...

...I saw that the new outfit arrived,
and... I was just looking at it...

...I feel happy that we'll
all have matching outfits...

...I see. Yeah, that's right. Soon, you'll wear
this outfit and stand on stage with everyone.
